{"tid":2458232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【12 港人】 7 人今提堂　須檢疫全部缺席　案件押後再訊","createTime":"2021-03-23T09:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T11:15:51.000Z","uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1b17f6c57fd1d7ba99897694a6159f798fc75619","tid":2458232,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:15:19.000Z","msg":"「送中」12 港人中，被內地判監 7 個月的李宇軒等 8 人，昨( 22 日) 刑滿後即日經深圳灣移交香港警方。除了未被落案起訴的「香港故事」成員李宇軒，另外 7 人的案件今( 23 日) 分別於東區、粉嶺、屯門裁判法院及區域法院提訊。由於 7 人須隔離檢疫，都未有出庭應訊。12 港人關注組表示，至少 4 人仍未能與家人聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n屬同案被告的張俊富、張銘裕及嚴文謙案件，今早已於東區裁判法院提堂，3 人均無出庭應訊。控方透露，3 人正接受隔離檢疫，申請押後案件至 3 月31 日再訊。他們 2019 年 12 月 8 日在灣仔被捕，控以串謀意圖造成身體嚴重傷害而射擊罪。<br />\n<br />\n至於李子賢、鄭子豪所涉的案件，下午於區域法院提堂，兩人同樣缺席聆訊，控方申請案件押後至 4 月 8 日再訊，兩人並無申請保釋，期間須還押。<br />\n對於有報道引述消息指，8 人之中有部分人稱暫時不需要律師代表。12 港人關注組回應指，由於不希望影響法律程序，無法回答相關事宜。<br />\n8 人昨日返港後，12 港人關注組成員鄒幸彤批評警方沒向家屬交代交接安排，特首林鄭月娥今早回應指，警方必定會依法辦事，「一定唔會剝奪市民包括逃犯享有的權利」，又指於內地服刑完畢的 8 人返港後需繼續接受法律制裁，「因為佢哋本身係一個逃犯，在港犯事想逃離，唔去承擔法律責任」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/12-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91-4-%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA-%E9%A0%88%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2-%E6%B6%89%E6%A1%88%E6%8A%BC%E8%87%B3%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F12-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E7%25B5%2584-%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591-4-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%25A0%2588%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%258A%25BC%25E8%2587%25B3%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97YuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=3bec49a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F12-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E7%25B5%2584-%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591-4-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%25A0%2588%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%258A%25BC%25E8%2587%25B3%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&h=c04e7dec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/12-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91-4-%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA-%E9%A0%88%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2-%E6%B6%89%E6%A1%88%E6%8A%BC%E8%87%B3%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A/</a>"},{"pid":"5c952098685420680818c6f949d31d191c2fe29c","tid":2458232,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:16:27.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥今早回應指，警方必定會依法辦事，「一定唔會剝奪市民包括逃犯享有的權利」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d0b65c0ef2be2c84600b6c7b3e74d9230c995e","tid":2458232,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />cls"},{"pid":"ec1bb71f7c835dfc7134997b36d86f7106072914","tid":2458232,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fe16e93d2ef4b69026513133f884560cfbc9e5","t